{"tid":1590110,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"26/9 又有得同林鄭師妹拖手仔","createTime":"2019-09-23T14:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T02:50:56.000Z","uid":2917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3557dc368fb7cabf5d232dbe48511f171f2d50ba","tid":1590110,"uid":2917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"市民對政權反對的聲音此起彼落，但林鄭仍然視若無睹，用社區對話去轉移焦點，妄想示威者會分化最終失敗，避開回應五大訴求。<br />\n-<br />\n我等中學生，作為社會的未來棟樑，無懼警黑打壓。這一次，香港鄧鏡波書院，嘉諾撒聖方濟各書院，香港華仁書院，聖公會鄧肇堅中學，鄧肇堅維多利亞官立中學，香港真光中學，六校同學和舊生在社區對話會議前夕和期間，以和平，理性，非暴力的形式在會場附近組成人鏈，要求港府正面回應市民訴求，承認警隊肆意襲擊市民之問題並道歉。<br />\n-<br />\n日期: 26/9<br />\n集合時間: 16:30<br />\n集合地點：東華百年廣場（St. Joe 小學對面）<br />\n服飾:舊生黑衫 就讀學生校服<br />\n必備物品:長遮,口罩,Gear(如有）<br />\n-<br />\n伊館人鏈Channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAESd6KDkOfk7C9qppw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAESd6KDkOfk7C9qppw&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=e20c8f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAESd6KDkOfk7C9qppw</a><br />\n-<br />\n伊館人鏈公海<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LieYvBfMv8m7MFaai2wW7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLieYvBfMv8m7MFaai2wW7A&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obvUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=4c7cd301\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LieYvBfMv8m7MFaai2wW7A</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yB07f1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyB07f1H.jpg&h=c6e5cd58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"034753dba3cc2ed1d6c57177788636318d7f1947","tid":1590110,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{